title: McFarlane's: Warrior of the Zodiac - Taurus
description: From Todd McFarlane comes an entirely new take on Zodiac mythology. Warriors of the Zodiac is in the year of the Zodiac, featuring figures inspired by all twelve astrological signs. Taurus is articulated at neck, shoulders, wrists, waist and ankles. Includes removable mask and weapon. Collect them all.
